Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.98,0:01:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我與艾莉發現特雷斯\n小時後的玩伴雪希莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然在幫戈圖的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.55,0:01:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翁先生逼的我與比查他們\n不得不單獨行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.13,0:01:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於不能連港口也破壞掉\n才讓戈圖他免於全滅的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.71,0:01:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來特雷斯還把雪希莉亞\n帶回到亞加碼,問題大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.02,0:02:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十一話 愛哭鬼雪希莉亞 下集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.15,0:02:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...我再想待久一點也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.45,0:02:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你再吃驚什麼?\n不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.33,0:02:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.54,0:02:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下,你想去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.12,0:02:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在亞加碼裏面不可以亂跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.35,0:02:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到她在披薩店後面\n跟戈圖說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾利!\n雪希莉亞..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.81,0:02:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我什麼都不知道\n別哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒拍下地圖,我什麼都沒做,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.91,0:02:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放我回家吧,求求你,特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.81,0:02:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,艦長呢?\n不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.48,0:02:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去問他該怎麼處理雪希莉亞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.56,0:02:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,我會被逮捕嗎?\n應該吧..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是沒辦法的\n特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.11,0:02:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前我還不確定\n可是如果你說的是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.96,0:03:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會拜託艦長放你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.29,0:03:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們犯錯,導致現在沒半架MS可動用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,戈圖大人\n別狡辯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.53,0:03:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,三架增援的MS來到\n格拉納達附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一齊出動攻打亞加瑪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.31,0:03:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不知道亞加瑪躲在格拉那達哪個角落的情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.23,0:03:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼用四架MS去打阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.74,0:03:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖大人,隔壁的貨船\n要求我們賠償損失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了,要錢就給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.72,0:03:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼會想到這個主意呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.91,0:03:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,買下港口所有的貨船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.03,0:03:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那些船都毀的快不能動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照我的指示做就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.72,0:03:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是個好計劃\n阿哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.82,0:04:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看著吧就算沒有\n姬娜大人在,我還是會達成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.73,0:04:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感冒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.76,0:04:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你們把我當俘虜\n可是我還是有洗衣服,你不能虧待我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是來談判那件事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要放我出去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.17,0:04:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這艘船再過半天就要出航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.14,0:04:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前,請你住進\n格拉那達的俘虜收容所,這是命令書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.80,0:04:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,我喜歡這艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.15,0:04:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經盡力做好俘虜的工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.08,0:04:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然...要我安慰艦長也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣\n你害羞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手\n你吃醋了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.97,0:04:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別把我和你這老女人混為一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老女人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.21,0:04:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長\n嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不方便嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有不方便!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.19,0:04:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這艘船有與戈圖接觸...\n戈圖來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.02,0:04:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那跟你無關\n他是我的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.84,0:04:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.93,0:05:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,間諜是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞,特雷斯的童年玩伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.80,0:05:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前還不能斷言\n可能是有苦衷而...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.61,0:05:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪個間諜沒有苦衷呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.20,0:05:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的戈圖,他要是擊毀格拉那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使哈曼大人無法用來作基地看他怎麼交代..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼想拿這裏當做基地嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有說過那句話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.15,0:05:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是\n艦長在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是MS?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.72,0:05:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,是安多拉的MS!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪的是還有四艘運輸船接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.91,0:05:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒進入港口吧\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.89,0:05:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別過來,不然我就讓她眼睛瞎掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.24,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是說真的\n你太卑鄙了,姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.97,0:05:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為你能空手逃走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.80,0:06:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆\n我不會一直洗衣服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.40,0:06:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦內發出緊急警報\n姬娜抓走人質逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備隨時啟航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.36,0:06:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.78,0:06:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,放開我\n沒那麼簡單!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.34,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快抓住姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.71,0:06:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請放開我\n少囉唆,進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.59,0:06:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒體會這感覺了\NMS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1,2...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.70,0:06:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准碰我的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.09,0:06:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還找到槍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不乖乖打開艙口,我就殺死這個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手!救命啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別打開艙口,你想讓姬娜逃走嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.68,0:07:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.09,0:07:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.91,0:07:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上來..\n特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達,出動\n知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,放我下去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別哭叫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.78,0:07:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的人會阻止MS的\n然後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.32,0:07:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個間諜太無禮了\n我沒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.27,0:07:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必須帶我去見戈圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.49,0:07:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留在這裏你會被槍決的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然了,你是間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裏上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.22,0:07:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停住了\n港口停電嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.32,0:08:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖發動攻擊了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.06,0:08:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那個不是亞加瑪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.07,0:08:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它沒這麼簡單就出來的\n用船擊毀港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.98,0:08:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後它一定會跑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.88,0:08:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的戈圖\n他真的想毀了格拉那達嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.33,0:08:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的家人還在格拉那達\n你太囉唆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些人用貨船攻擊港口,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想把我們逼出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.44,0:08:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,港口遭到破壞的話\n空氣會流失的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.70,0:08:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿雷射槍,我要阻止戈圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密通道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.72,0:09:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管這麼多了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,太狹窄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mk-ll在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.98,0:09:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,街市用的出入口\nMS是無法使用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.05,0:09:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.83,0:09:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想被砍頭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.47,0:09:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是槍決嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.82,0:09:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.44,0:09:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我不想被逮捕\n不會的,你不會有危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.41,0:09:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,格拉那達..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.68,0:09:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是停電而已\n不逃走我會死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別走,雪希莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜交給你們處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.25,0:09:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯!\n我必須阻止戈圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.24,0:10:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,22號碼頭有行動了\n瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走哪裏才能到外面呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.03,0:10:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是...這是阿納海\n不..不會錯的,是阿納海的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生產線一時停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.53,0:10:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於電力不足,生產線一時停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.48,0:10:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作業人員請到避難區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作業人員請到避難區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.16,0:10:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.46,0:10:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派貨船到33號碼頭\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.63,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是卡西歐移民船的船票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照約定的人數一個也沒少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.19,0:11:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下,帶這個走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面的金塊算是特別報酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可輕易打開\n免的受人懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.88,0:11:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...辛苦你了,謝謝\n不好意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.41,0:11:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,33號碼頭的船沉沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪應該無法出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.53,0:11:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯!媽媽,你先走\n沒時間了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.20,0:12:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你去通知戈圖了嗎\n特雷斯,我還是你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你不是要坐移民船嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.75,0:12:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心,我說好了\n船票我拿到了,特雷斯,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.62,0:12:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起走我才不怕,這樣你也不必再打仗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我坐視\n亞加瑪的人死掉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.41,0:12:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我騙他亞加瑪在33號碼頭\n所以沒問題的,特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.51,0:12:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞你怎麼會這樣的?那個碼頭的人死掉\n也無所謂嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.06,0:12:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且33號碼頭是最靠近格拉那達\n市區的碼頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.85,0:13:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人逃走會心虛\n所以你想帶我ㄧ起逃走嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.41,0:13:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的,特雷斯,我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任性的女人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.22,0:13:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便你滾到別的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.25,0:13:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯!你走了的話,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.84,0:13:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去求神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.24,0:13:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,神總是欺負我\n我只有你阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.29,0:13:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我討厭自私自利的愛哭鬼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.21,0:13:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有你的家人就夠了\n家人對我而言是重擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.67,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.37,0:13:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,敵人擊毀33號碼頭了\n那地方很靠近市區阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,尼路..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.44,0:14:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何ZZ高達會在這裏的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.22,0:14:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達不是應該在33號碼頭裏的嗎\n快躲起來,克雷優!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.87,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖大人,船全用光了\n怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.64,0:14:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,27號碼頭有艘卡西歐移民船會開出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.38,0:14:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那艘船逼往亞加瑪\n所在的碼頭,不要管ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.02,0:14:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡西歐號快啟航\n現在還可以脫離格拉那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒系安全帶的人請坐穩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.06,0:14:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本船即將開航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.13,0:14:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外面還在MS大戰\n這時候開什麼船?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.29,0:14:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法,都超載了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.26,0:15:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的男人是誰?雪希莉亞\n這跟爸爸無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.72,0:15:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼!女兒幹什麼事\n父親不用管嗎?都是你教導無方!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想以移民船為擋箭牌?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機首往右\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被包圍了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼在這時候打開?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.70,0:15:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?是不是錢的下面裝了炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.57,0:15:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉唆!我又不是自願要上船的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.57,0:16:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是雪希莉亞哇哇哭\n我才跟上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是炸彈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.55,0:16:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡西歐在上方擋著,在飛上去很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.46,0:16:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,用MS推走它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.70,0:16:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的真是簡單呢\n怎麼辦?捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.74,0:16:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不怕,特雷斯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.36,0:16:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再膽小下去,我就無法見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.31,0:16:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(你就不顧港口人們的安危嗎?)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.56,0:16:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯..\n(自私自利的愛哭鬼)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.05,0:16:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖大人,接近亞加瑪了\n會撞上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與亞加瑪保持距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.55,0:16:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答是\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.69,0:16:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.19,0:17:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種狀況下很難攻擊快狙擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.96,0:17:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.39,0:17:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布茲\n你太不會閃躲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你不在乎,別怪我不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.46,0:17:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯,我不會一直當愛哭鬼的\n特雷斯...我不怕,我才不怕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克雷優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我能拋棄父母的話..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.28,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(你不在乎城裏的人嗎?)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.07,0:18:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,在這裏不行阿,特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攜帶用飛行器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.86,0:18:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你想辦法引開卡西歐號\n特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在嘗試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.77,0:18:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,現在卡西歐號客滿了\n特雷斯,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼路,回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.18,0:18:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是克雷優...\n你想被爆炸波及嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.67,0:18:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.28,0:18:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點移動吧,快點離的更遠吧\n這樣我就可以丟掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.51,0:18:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.73,0:18:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有東西掉在機身上面\n沒有損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿...選這時候跑掉你死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.08,0:19:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?是一般市民的太空衣\n快離開!喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.71,0:19:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始倒數\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是姬娜大人\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.13,0:19:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人...擊毀ZZ高達後\n我們馬上回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請稍後一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.56,0:19:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想開貨船來救我?\n戈圖那傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞\n那不是雪希莉亞嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.83,0:19:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS追過來了,不行\n不可以靠近這個MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼?喂,雪希莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.68,0:20:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯說討厭自私的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.10,0:20:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度好像想追到\n戈圖潛伏的港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各隊MS準備出發\n遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.66,0:20:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能輸,絕不能輸\n我不是膽小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要阿!雪希莉亞\n我知道你想做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼路把敵人的MS引過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想找出我們的藏身之處嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把大炮對準ZZ高達\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.09,0:20:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是雪希莉亞吧?快下來,我來接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.21,0:20:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,那樣會被特雷斯討厭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要證明我不是膽小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.36,0:20:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達居然沒注意到\n戈圖大人的船在正前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會措手不及的\n我先把你的腳砍下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大炮瞄準!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.70,0:21:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.94,0:21:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.32,0:21:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別過來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達,在會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.13,0:21:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞在那裏\n我什麼事也不能做阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.98,0:21:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達不能動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.06,0:21:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊,把他打下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.69,0:21:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次你死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.93,0:21:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特雷斯..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪希莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈...戈圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.90,0:21:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說亞古捷斯的軍人在上面\n那真是罪有應得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.51,0:21:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是中繼回線的影像\n敵人MS一起消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.29,0:21:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.80,0:22:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,敵人自己爆炸的\n我們運氣真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.26,0:22:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(卡西歐號平安無事了\n雪希莉亞,你的運氣轉好了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.15,0:22:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(忘記不愉快的過去\n到新殖民地要好好努力阿)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.41,0:22:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼...為什麼這樣?\n自己做下這麼傻的判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.51,0:23:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧古的參謀總部明明不在戰場中 卻處處命令著我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.55,0:23:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼在靜止衛星軌道展開的艦隊規模很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.70,0:23:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會死的可是我們這邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.59,0:24:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 我們這邊放手去幹你們也沒話說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.50,0:24:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 捷度 出擊！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.39,0:24:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼小姐 真的很漂亮啊

